summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Water Department authorizing the sale and conveyance by Quit Claim Deed of a portion of real property commonly known as the Lake Youngs Aquaduct Right-of-Way (LYA R/W) located in Section 23, Township 22 North, Range 6 East, W.M., King County, Washington, to Clinton L. Spaulding and M. Randi Spaulding, husband and wife.
